<refsect1>
    <title>Description</title>

    <note><para>This plugin is not enabled by default, as it is superseded by the Video 4 Linux 2 plugin.  To enable it, configure Camunits with <literal>--with-v4l1-plugin</literal></para></note>

    <para>
    <literal>input.v4l</literal> provides access to Video 4 Linux 1 devices.
    </para>

